378
00:20:08,250 --> 00:20:09,833
Can't be. Uh!

379
00:20:12,375 --> 00:20:13,291
[ALL] Huh?

380
00:20:13,375 --> 00:20:14,916
[music from game]

381
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:16,375
Oh yeah!

382
00:20:17,458 --> 00:20:19,500
[MAN groans]

383
00:20:19,583 --> 00:20:21,583
[MALE OPERATOR G groans]

384
00:20:21,666 --> 00:20:23,083
[MALE OPERATOR H grunts]

385
00:20:23,166 --> 00:20:32,333
♪

386
00:20:32,416 --> 00:20:35,708
It's game on now,
